main event: Witnesses reported seeing a white, circular object in Temple, Texas in June 1961.
interesting points: The object was similar to a star but larger and brighter,The sighting lasted for about 1-2 minutes with varying durations reported,Multiple forms of observations were documented from different dates involving similar objects,Some possibilities of misidentification with known astronomical objects were suggested,The UFO report is part of Project Blue Book's documentation process.
witness description: witnesses saw a bright circular object in the sky, at times described as ovoid and star-like
